title: Free Chopin concert
text: Sunshine, lots of people and a grand piano playing Chopin. The park is an oasis in the city and being able to listen to these masterpieces by Chopin is very soothing

title: Tourist trap
text: One of many restaurants in a square in the old town. Was no major difference from any other restaurant. Good service and ordinary Polish dishes

title: Lot of tourist´s
text: Nice place with a lot of tourist´s and restaurant´s. Price level high, but a must do if you visit Warsaw.

title: Good standard
text: Hotel close to airport, one station by train. New, fresh hotel with bed not so soft. Very good breakfast, hot and cold dishes. Good communication to city (walk about 600 m to tram 17 and 18). Will book this next time in Warsaw.

title: A nice place with a good service
text: Ocean view, high and good music. Friendly staff provide a good service.Ate a snapper that was a little dry

title: A very good pizza
text: One of the best pizza, a little spicy tomato sauce taste very good. A good chioce of topping. Nice atmosphere

title: I recommend this place
text: Recommend this. Very good with a delicious quality of food. Nice atmosphere and good service. If you are nearby, so it is a must to visit this

title: Nice area to walk in
text: Many nice restaurants and small shops. Above all you see Acropolis. This part of Athens is a must visit

title: Now we talking about history
text: If you are in Athens this must be on your bucket list. We decided to visit the Acropolis on a very hot day, the queue to the entrance was very long. In the queue we received an offer to accompany a guide, cost a little extra but definitely worth it. Got a guided tour up the mountain, the Acropolis itself we got to discover by ourselves. Great view from the top

title: Nice hotel in a great location near metro
text: Very closed to metro Omonia. Nice room with comfortable beds and a well-functioning A/C. Staff could be more helpful and engaged. Breakfast OK, but the breakfast room was very impersonal. A bottle of wine at the room when we arrived was appreciated

title: Nice hotel very close to the beach
text: Nice hotel very close to the beach. Very nice staff who were helpful. To have breakfast with a view across the sea was wonderful. No breakfast buffet, it is served at the table. Comfortable beds and a lovely balcony with sea view. We will be happy to return.
